  <div class="row j5 white" id="Scarf">
    <div class="head-3">
      <h3>4. Scarf Process</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-4 sm-space half-content">
        <img src="/assets/images/togogames/Scarf2.png" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 sm-space half-content">
        <img src="/assets/images/togogames/Scarf1.png" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 sm-space half-content">
        <img src="/assets/images/togogames/Scarf3.png" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-sm-8 half-content">
        <div>I started working on another wearable game, a scarf that used the theme of travel for the users. It used coins instead of pieces so that parts would be easy to find. I developed a magnetic pin version of the Pop-o-matic.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 half-content xs-space">

